{"lemma":"حالِقُ","slug":"حالِقُ","root":"ح.ل.ق","root_slug":"ح-ل-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ل-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8889"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%90%D9%82%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8889","headword_ar":"حَالِقٌ","root":"Hlq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Shaving:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a shaver;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a shearer"},{"kind":"text","text":"of goats: (T, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaqapN","text_ar":"حَلَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, S, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hal~aAqN","text_ar":"حَلَّاقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAliqN","text_ar":"حَالِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [or has an intensive signification, or denotes frequency of the action.] The saying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tafoEalo *aAka A^um~uka HaAliqN","text_ar":"لَا تَفْعَلْ ذَاكَ اُمُّكَ حَالِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do not thou that:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may"},{"kind":"text","text":"God cause"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy mother"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be bereft of her child so that she shall"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shave off her hair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAliqapN","text_ar":"حَالِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a trad. as an epithet applied to a woman cursed by Mohammad; (TA;) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who shaves off her hair in the case of an affliction:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who shares her face for the sake of embellishment."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) It is also applied to a wound on the head ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aj~apN","text_ar":"شَجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That scrapes off the skin from the flesh."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dmg","text_ar":"دمغ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sharp;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a knife: (TA:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAluwqapN","text_ar":"حَالُوقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; applied to a sword; and also to a man. (Ibn-'Abbád, K.) [Hence, perhaps,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN HaAliqN A_ilaY~a biEayonihi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ حَالِقٌ اـِلَىَّ بِعَيْنِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is looking at me intently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharply;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHal~iqN","text_ar":"مُحَلِّقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"znr","text_ar":"زنر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swift; and light, active,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agile."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light of flesh; slender, and lean;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lean, and lank in the belly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  Accord. to A'Obeyd and the K, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An udder:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and accord. to the K, it means also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) but it is an epithet applied to an udder; and thus applied, it has this latter meaning, i. e. (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, TA;) so ISd thinks; (TA;) as though the milk in it reached to its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloq","text_ar":"حَلْق"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"big, so that it rubs off the hair of the thighs by reason of its bigness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and it has also the contr. meaning; (T, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raised"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T, Kr, ISd, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"towards the belly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, ISd, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Kr, ISd, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that its milk has become scanty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has gone away:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, ISd, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hul~aqN","text_ar":"حُلَّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawaAliqu","text_ar":"حَوَالِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaqapN","text_ar":"حَلَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA. [The last is mentioned as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HAlq","text_ar":"حالق"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the latter sense.]) Accord. to As,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaHato Dar~apu Aln~aAqapi HaAliqFA","text_ar":"اَصْبَحَتْ ضَرَّةُ النَّاقَةِ حَالِقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel's udder became nearly full."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN HaAlqN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ حَالقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel having much milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having great abundance of milk, and a large udder:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_bilN muHal~iqapN","text_ar":"اـبِلٌ مُحَلِّقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camels having much milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(En-Nadr, TA:) and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HAlq","text_ar":"حالق"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawaAliqu","text_ar":"حَوَالِقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hul~aqN","text_ar":"حُلَّقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b6-  (tropical:)  A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high"},{"kind":"text","text":"mountain, (S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rising above what surrounds it, and without vegetable produce:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say, a mountain"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having no vegetable produce;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it were shaven, or shorn; of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but Z says that it is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hal~aqa","text_ar":"حَلَّقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a bird: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an overtopping"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overlooking, place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawaY mino HaAliqK","text_ar":"هَوَى مِنْ حَالِقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fell from a high to a low place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 37.) And its pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuluqN","text_ar":"حُلُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vacant spaces between heaven and earth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unlucky"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to a people;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though peeling them; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAliqapN","text_ar":"حَالِقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to the copies of the K; but correctly ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAluwqapN","text_ar":"حَالُوقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the O and Tekmileh. (TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tendril,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twining portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a grape-vine, (S, K, TA,) and of a colocynth and the like, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hanging to the shoots:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:) because it has a circular form, like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloqap","text_ar":"حَلْقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or ring]. (T, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["T","TA","S","K","IAar","Kr","ISd"]}]}}